resources.string: The Originals is a television series that premiered on The CW in 2013 and ran for five seasons until 2018. The show is a spinoff of the popular series The Vampire Diaries and focuses on the Mikaelson family, a group of ancient vampires who return to their former home of New Orleans after being exiled for centuries.

However, they quickly discover that the city is no longer the same as they remember it, and they must navigate a complex web of alliances, enemies, and old grudges in order to achieve their goals.
